{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/genericonoffsetunacknowledged\/continuetransaction"]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/GenericOnOffSetUnacknowledged\/continueTransaction"},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","externalID":"s:10NordicMesh18TransactionMessagePAAE08continueC0Sbvp::SYNTHESIZED::s:10NordicMesh29GenericOnOffSetUnacknowledgedV","role":"symbol","extendedModule":"NordicMesh","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"continueTransaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"title":"continueTransaction","modules":[{"name":"NordicMesh"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/GenericOnOffSetUnacknowledged"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Whether the message should start a new transaction."}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"continueTransaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The messages within a transaction carry the cumulative values of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a field. In case one or more messages within a transaction are not","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"received by the Server (e.g., as a result of radio collisions),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the next received message will make up for the lost messages,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"carrying cumulative values of the field.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A new transaction is started when this field is set to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or when the last message of the transaction was sent 6 or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"more seconds earlier.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"},{"type":"text","text":", which means that each new message will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"receive a new transaction identifier (if not set explicitly)."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/GenericOnOffSetUnacknowledged/continueTransaction":{"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"continueTransaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/GenericOnOffSetUnacknowledged\/continueTransaction","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/genericonoffsetunacknowledged\/continuetransaction","title":"continueTransaction","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Whether the message should start a new transaction.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh":{"abstract":[{"text":"Provision, configure and control Bluetooth mesh devices with nRF Mesh library.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"NordicMesh","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/GenericOnOffSetUnackno